# GĐ3+4 Frontend Data Fetching + Render Tuning — Implementation Plan

> **For agentic workers:** REQUIRED SUB-SKILL: Use superpowers:subagent-driven-development (recommended) or superpowers:executing-plans to implement this plan task-by-task. Steps use checkbox (`- [ ]`) syntax for tracking.

**Goal:** Centralize frontend data fetching qua TanStack Query + API client, lazy load heavy modules (xlsx, recharts), virtualize bảng lớn — đạt First Load JS ≥30% giảm trên ≥1 admin route.

**Architecture:** Big-bang foundation (W1) tạo `lib/api/`, `lib/hooks/`, `<QueryProvider>` 1 lần dùng cho toàn app. Sau đó wave-based migration: W2 lazy load (low-risk wins), W3 top-pain admin pages, W4 virtualize, W5 màn hình còn lại. Mỗi wave 1 PR riêng để rollback dễ.

**Tech Stack:** Next.js 16 App Router, React 19, TypeScript, TanStack Query v5, TanStack Virtual v3, MSW v2, Jest + RTL.

**Spec:** `docs/superpowers/specs/2026-05-06-giai-doan-3-4-frontend-data-fetching-render-tuning-design.md`

